data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom, 2-story home with a 2-car garage – a perfect blend of comfort and style! As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the elegance of tile flooring that spans the main level, creating a seamless and inviting atmosphere. The heart of the home, the kitchen, boasts a delightful island with seating around, providing the ideal spot for gatherings or casual meals. The kitchen also features an oversized pantry, offering ample storage for all your culinary essentials. Upstairs, you'll find the tranquil bedrooms, providing a private retreat for each member of the household. The laundry room is conveniently located on the upper level, equipped with shelves, cabinets, and plenty of space to make laundry a breeze.With thoughtful design and practical features, this home is not just a residence but a sanctuary. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours – schedule a showing today and experience the comfort and convenience this home has to offer!
